See also blogpost.py man page.

PREREQUISITES
-------------
- http://www.methods.co.nz/asciidoc/[AsciiDoc].
- The http://code.google.com/p/wordpress-library/[Python
  Wordpress library]. To download and install:

  $ svn co http://wordpress-library.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ wordpress-library
  $ cd wordpress-library
  $ sudo python setup.py install


INSTALLATION
------------
- Download from http://TODO
- Put `blogpost.py` in search path (optional).
- Put `conf/wordpress.conf` in AsciiDoc install, global configuration
  or user (`$HOME/.asciidoc`) directory.
- Create `$HOME/.blogpost` configuration file (see example
  `conf/blogpost_example.conf`).


